```{r libraries, echo = FALSE, include = FALSE}
library(dplyr)
```

```{r preprocessing}
rm(list = ls())

# Load data from a .txt file
imported <- read.delim("data/cdi_percentile/percentiles_manybabies_cdi.txt") 

data <- tibble(vocabulary_percentile = imported$daily_percentile, ids_pref = imported$IDS_pref, test_age = imported$age_days, cdi_age = imported$CDI.agedays, protocol = imported$method, gender = imported$gender, lab = imported$labid, participant = imported$subid)
```
